<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10203118>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5–9. Lestiphorus. 5, 7–9—L. bilunulatus A. Costa (5, 7, 8—from Primorsky Terr., Russia, 9—fromAmur Prov., Russia); 6—L. yamatonis Tsuneki (from Kunashir Isl.); 5, 6—mesosoma, ventrolateral view, ♀; 7—metasoma, dorsolateral view, ♀; 8, 9—head, frontal view, ♀ (8), ♂ (9)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10203118/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10203114>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–4. Lestiphorus yamatonis Tsuneki (from Kunashir Isl.): 1—habitus, ♀; 2—propodeum and metasomal base, dor- solateral view, ♀; 3–4—head, frontal view, ♀ (3), ♂ (4)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10203114/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

